ABOUT_US_DOCTOR_SECTION1_P2: Saluber MD yakagadzirirwa kugadzirisa hukama hwechiremba-varwere kuburikidza nekugadzira 24/7 kuwana kwehutano pasi rose.
about_us_section1_p1: SaluberMD isangano reDynamic Health rakatsaurirwa kushandura kuendeswa kwezvipatara nemishonga yekuvandudza mararamiro ezvehutano munyika yose. Our Digital Medical Concierge services, kupa rubatsiro rwehutano uye hutano hwakanaka, vanachiremba vane chiremba vakagadziriswa, mapepa ezvokurapa mumitauro 18, zvipfeko zvekutarisa utano hwako, nekusvika kune unyanzvi hwevashandi vehutano nehutano.
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P1:
Kuburikidza neGoo-localization svondo redu richawana murapi wepamusoro pedyo newe. SaluberMD Physicians vanogona kuongorora, kubata, kana kukurukura nezvehutano hwehutano kuburikidza nevhidhiyo uye kukupa chirongwa chakakodzera chekurapa. Zvizhinji zvezvakawanda zvakajairika zvinotarisirwa muhofisi yechiremba zvinogona kurapwa nevhidhiyo kushanyira.
Mimwe yemamiriro edu atinotarisa:
ABOUT_US_SECTION2_P2: Nyaya Yenyu Yezvokurapa Ndiyo nzvimbo yakakodzera yekuchengetedza yese yehutano hwako, zvidhori uye mafaira. Chengeta ruzivo rwehutano hwako ne 24/7 kupinda kune mamwe marekete ezvekurapa. Pasinei nokuti uri pamba kana kuenda kune dzimwe nyika mashoko ako ari pamunwe wako kugovana nehutano hwako hwehutano. Izvo nyore kushandisa ruzivo rwomunhu wehutano hunowanikwa mumitauro 18.
ABOUT_US_SECTION3_P1: Ndiwo chete wepamusoro webazi rakagadziriswa Vanachiremba vanopa rubatsiro paSaluberMD. Aya maitiro anosimbiswa, akanyatsoongororwa uye akadzidziswa kupa hutano hwepamusoro. Chiremba mumwe nomumwe ane bio paunokwanisa kuona maitiro avo, zvidzidzo, uye ruzivo. SaluberMD yakagadzirirwa kuhutungamiri hwehutano hwakanaka hweViongorori vedu. A rating system inobvumira varwere kuti vaongorore vanachiremba uye kuti vaone vanachiremba zviyero zvachose.

QUALITY_INDEX_DESCRIPTION: Kuita muviri kwakakwana ndiko kwekutsungirira uye kushungurudzika kwepfungwa kunosangana nepamusoro pekukwanisa kugadzirisa uye kugadzirisa mamiriro acho ezvinhu. Nhengo yehutano yehutano inoratidza muviri wevanhu kuti uenderane nekuchinja kwezvakatipoteredza uye kushungurudzika kwekusimudzira, kuchengeta nekudzorera hutano hwehutano. Kuziva muviri kunowanzoonekwa mukukwanisa kwehupenyu hwevanhu, kudzidza, nekushanda, asiwo zvepanyama mukurovedza muviri. Unhu hwomunhu hunobatana nehutano asi hune hukama hwepedyo nekuwana chikafu uye muviri wekurovedza muviri. Achishandisa nzira dzakarurama uye maitiro akanaka, iye / iye anogona kuvandudza hukama hwake mumuviri mune zvose.

ssi_desc: Nokuongorora kufanana kwekushaya kwemoyo yenyu tinofananidza nehuwandu hwekunetseka. Kushungurudzika kunoita sekunowedzera kana kuwedzera mungozi yemamiriro ezvinhu sekurema, chirwere chemwoyo, chirwere cheAlzheimer, chirwere cheshuga, kuora mwoyo, matambudziko emimba, uye mafi. Ichengetedze iri pasi pe20 kuti uve parutivi rwakachengeteka!

tipshealt2: Kunyange zvazvo chirwere chepiruru hachiwanzoiti zvachose kudzivirirwa, zvakakosha kuwana. ICDC (Centers for Disease Control and Prevention) inokurudzira vachengetedzo yegore negore kune munhu wese ane makore matanhatu kana kupfuura. Kurwisa kunonyanya kukosha kune vanhu vari pangozi yakawanda yehutano hwehutano, kusanganisira
tipshealt5: Vana vaduku (pasi pemakore mana uye pamusoro pemwedzi 6)
tipshealt6: Chiito chepanyama chinowedzera chiyeuchidzo uye unyanzvi hwokufunga
tipshealt7: Kuita zvekuita nguva dzose kunogona kuvandudza uropi hunoita hupenyu hupenyu hwose uye kuderedza dambudziko rekuora mwoyo.
tipshealt8: Zvidzidzo zvakasiyana-siyana zvakabudiswa pakusangana kwepedyo uye kubatsirwa kwekuita zvekuita nguva dzose uye kugadziriswa kugadzirisa basa.
tipshealt9: Izvozvo zvinosangana zvakananga muuropi uye zvisina kurongeka kuburikidza nezviito zvemagetsi uye zvemuviri pamuviri.
